      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_6470D3B0-1ED7-0135-1092-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In order to filter your Calendar by courses or groups, click the color box next to the Calendar [1]. The calendar can show up to 10 courses and/or groups at a time. In this example, not all of the calendars are being shown.</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>Canvas will assign an arbitrary color for each calendar unless a custom color is chosen. Each calendar contains 15 default colors, but you can create any color of your choice by selecting the <strong>More</strong> icon [2] and inserting a Hex code [3].</p>
